"We will also be discussing and practicing teaching techniques to create a positive and\n"
"welcoming environment in your classrooms."
msgstr ""

#: instructor-training/_episodes/01-welcome.md:144
# header
msgid "### Carpentry History and Culture"
msgstr ""

#: instructor-training/_episodes/01-welcome.md:146
msgid "We will be introducing you to the teaching practices that have been\n"
