">\n"
"> This exercise and discussion should take about 5 minutes."
msgstr ""

#: instructor-training/_episodes/09-mindset.md:144
# header
msgid "## Perseverance Predicts Success"
msgstr ""

#: instructor-training/_episodes/09-mindset.md:146
msgid "Finally, have you ever thought about how the quality of persistence can\n"
"impact someone's learning?"
msgstr ""

#: instructor-training/_episodes/09-mindset.md:149
msgid "Angela Duckworth, a Psychology professor from University of Pennsylvania, suggests that something called *grit* is an essential trait in\n"
"learning. Grit can be defined as [perseverance and passion in the face of difficulty towards a defined long term goal](https://www.dropbox.com/s/cvg1mbz0xrfx25l/DuckworthGross2014.pdf).\n"
"Learners with grit are willing to fail in their pursuit if they feel that it gets them closer to their goal. Learning and recovering\n"
"from failure is an essential skill in many fields. Learners with grit have shown to have a higher degree of success later on in\n"
"life. However, grit is not an innate trait; there is much evidence that suggests that grit is a trait that can be learned and instilled in\n"
"learners."
msgstr ""

#: instructor-training/_episodes/09-mindset.md:156
msgid "There are many ways we can help our learners attain grit."
msgstr ""

#: instructor-training/_episodes/09-mindset.md:158
# unordered list
msgid "- *Modeling resilience by sharing experiences of struggle*. Sharing your own experiences of having difficulty learning certain computing"
msgstr ""

#: instructor-training/_episodes/09-mindset.md:159
msgid "concepts may help learners understand that the process of learning can be difficult. Sharing failures that were learning experiences may aid in\n"
"modeling resilience.\n"
"- *Promoting Perseverance*. Part of grit is being able to push through even when things are difficult. Improvement-based praise is an\n"
"important motivating tool to promote perseverance.\n"
"- *Sharing Passion*. Talking about why you persist in working in your field despite the difficulties and challenges is another way to instill\n"
"grit.\n"
"- *Emphasizing Long-Term Goals*. Showing the effects of learning the concepts in terms of learners' individual long-term goals can instill\n"
"passion and drive for learning despite the difficulties of the topic."
msgstr ""

#: instructor-training/_episodes/09-mindset.md:168
# blockquote, which can be cascaded
msgid "> ## How Are You Gritty? (Optional)"
msgstr ""

#: instructor-training/_episodes/09-mindset.md:170
