msgid "You can refer to the lists of [Software Carpentry lessons](https://software-carpentry.org/lessons/), [Data Carpentry lessons](http://www.datacarpentry.org/lessons/), and [Library Carpentry lessons](https://librarycarpentry.org/lessons/) on the websites.\n"
