msgid "### Host abilities:  "
msgstr ""

#: instructor-training/_extras/guide.md:150
# unordered list
msgid "- “Mute” is in the lower left. To mute other participants, the host can go to “Manage Participants”, hover over a participant’s name, and click “mute”.  "
msgstr ""

